        <updateDate>2009-06-10T20:37:58Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>United States-Afghanistan Security and Stability Act - Directs the President to develop and transmit to the appropriate congressional committees, with intelligence support from the Director of National Intelligence, a comprehensive interagency strategy and implementation plan for long-term security and stability in Afghanistan. </p> <p>Authorizes appropriations for Afghanistan.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
